## Dashboard KPIs (computed from API data)

Fetch on mount: `/inventory`, `/campaigns`, `/bookings`, activity from seed.

| KPI | Formula |
|-----|---------|
| Total Units | `inventory.length` |
| Occupancy Rate | `booked / total * 100`% |
| Active Campaigns | `campaigns.filter(c=>c.status==='active').length` |
| Revenue MTD | sum of active booking `monthly_rate` (simplified; label "Est. Revenue MTD") |

Recharts `<AreaChart>` or `<BarChart>` for occupancy trend — use static week-labels + computed values from booking counts by type (billboard/dooh/truckside). Chart height 220px, fill `--accent` with 20% opacity.

Activity feed: `GET /activity` not exposed — use 8 seeded activity strings from db.ts as static array in Dashboard mock, or add a `/activity` route. Simpler: hardcode the 8 recent events from seed as mock activity in the Dashboard component (no new endpoint needed).

